                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2603.17512/2603.17512v1/x1.png",
                "caption": "Figure 1:Overview of XBridge. Pretrained multilingual NMT models provide broad language coverage but limited general reasoning capability, while English-centric LLMs excel at general reasoning yet struggle with low-resource or unseen languages. XBridge harmonizes these strengths through model composition, offloading multilingual processing to the pretrained multilingual model while leveraging the LLM as a knowledge core.",
                "position": 322
            }
        ]
