                "caption": "Figure 2:Left:XBridge composes a pretrained multilingual encoder-decoder with an LLM via lightweight mapping layers for multilingual understanding and generation, keeping the LLM frozen as a knowledge core.Right:A three-stage training strategy progressively aligns heterogeneous representations and adapts the encoder and decoder.",
